== 教育背景 ==
杰特曼在[[不列颠哥伦比亚大学|不列颠哥伦比亚大学]]获得主修数学的理学士学位<ref name=23andme-pr />他于1988年获得[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]统计学博士学位；其答辩论文标题为《Exploratory methods for censored data》。<ref name="gentlemanphd">{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=Robert Clifford|last=Gentleman |title=Exploratory methods for censored data |publisher=University of Washington |date=1988 |url=http://search.proquest.com/docview/303589316|authorlink =Robert Gentleman (statistician)}}</ref>

== 研究 ==
